{
  "id": "63df5a06b72445001d2e3e9c",
  "title": "反証主義",
  "created": 1675581964,
  "updated": 1675582985,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63df5a06b72445001d2e3e9c",
      "text": "反証主義",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675581964,
      "updated": 1675581964
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5a0c71fa08000067797c",
      "text": "[カール・ポパー]が提唱した科学に関する考え([形而上学]的な立場の１つ)",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675581964,
      "updated": 1675582376
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5a9671fa080000677984",
      "text": " [科学]は、[反証可能性]が大事",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582102,
      "updated": 1675582206
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d9b71fa0800006779a2",
      "text": " 具体的には",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582876,
      "updated": 1675582878
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d9e71fa0800006779a3",
      "text": "  理論や仮説が科学的であるか否かの基準として、反証可能性を選択",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582879,
      "updated": 1675582894
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5dae71fa0800006779a4",
      "text": "  反証可能性を持つ仮説のみが科学的である",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582895,
      "updated": 1675582910
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5dbe71fa0800006779a5",
      "text": "  厳しい[反証テスト]に耐え抜いた仮説ほど信頼性が高い",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582910,
      "updated": 1675582927
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5b8271fa08000067798f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582338,
      "updated": 1675582338
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5af471fa080000677987",
      "text": "科学の目的",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582197,
      "updated": 1675582215
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5b0671fa080000677989",
      "text": " 科学は定説を反証しようと試みる行為である",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582215,
      "updated": 1675582225
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5b1071fa08000067798a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582225,
      "updated": 1675582451
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d4071fa08000067799b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582785,
      "updated": 1675582785
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5cd871fa080000677994",
      "text": "科学において大切なのは、反証する作業の方ということ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582680,
      "updated": 1675582786
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5c0971fa080000677990",
      "text": " 帰納法は正当化できない",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582474,
      "updated": 1675582702
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5c4171fa080000677991",
      "text": "  [ヒューム的懐疑]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582529,
      "updated": 1675582702
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5b6371fa08000067798d",
      "text": "  帰納法で導き出された命題は、必ず正しいということができない",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582308,
      "updated": 1675582702
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d0471fa080000677998",
      "text": "   帰納法で導出された命題を、仮説と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582724,
      "updated": 1675582732
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5c6f71fa080000677993",
      "text": " 演繹法は正当化できる",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582576,
      "updated": 1675582715
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5cfb71fa080000677997",
      "text": "  そして、仮説の反証は演繹を使用する",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582715,
      "updated": 1675582740
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d3471fa08000067799a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582773,
      "updated": 1675582773
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d5471fa08000067799d",
      "text": "ポパーは、反証主義的な観点から、[論理実証主義]を批判した",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582805,
      "updated": 1675582844
    },
    {
      "id": "63df5d5471fa08000067799e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1675582805,
      "updated": 1675582805
    },
